# Discord Bot Token
#
# Using a bot token gives you MUCH higher rate limits (5000 requests/10min vs 50/10min)
#
# How to get a bot token:
# 1. Go to https://discord.com/developers/applications
# 2. Click "New Application"
# 3. Give it a name (e.g., "Invite Scraper")
# 4. Go to the "Bot" section
# 5. Click "Add Bot"
# 6. Under "Token", click "Reset Token" and copy it
# 7. Paste your token below (remove the # comment symbol)
#
# IMPORTANT: Keep your token secret! Never share it or commit it to git
#
# Example (replace with your real token):
# YOUR_BOT_TOKEN_HERE

# Remove this file's .example extension and paste your token on a new line
